Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
get_visible_netGroups(25.10)                      get_visible_netGroups(25.10)

Name
       get_visible_netGroups  -  Returns the names of the visible netGroups if
       some netGroups have been hidden in the design

Syntax
       get_visible_netGroups

       [-help]

       Returns the names of the visible netGroups if some netGroups have  been
       hidden in the design. If all netGroups are visible, this command has no
       effect.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description that includes type and default infor-
              mation for each get_visible_netGroups parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man get_visible_netGroups

Examples
              * The  following  command  returns  the name of all visible net-
                Groups in the designs:

                innovus 17> get_visible_netGroups

                test_ng

Related Information
              * set_visible_netGroups

